column5: I'm watching John right now on the musky hunter great net job John.
He is used to it,,,lots of practice with me  I wish, I am usually the net man with John. It's about times the tables turned.
Lol for sure Greg. John got a very nice one that was a good episode. Well I gotta get ready to head off to Toronto. See ya tomorrow John
Very cool - amazing to see one of our own on the show!
Congrats John, it looked like you and Taro enjoyed yourselves, well done.
